11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_RENDER_QUEUE_ITEM_VERIFIER_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_RENDER_QUEUE_ITEM_VERIFIER_H_
13
14#include <vector>
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18// Functor to use when supplying a verifier function for the queue item
19// verifcation.
20template <typename T>
21class RenderQueueItemVerifier {
22 public:
23 explicit RenderQueueItemVerifier(size_t minimum_capacity)
24 : minimum_capacity_(minimum_capacity) {}
25
26 bool operator()(const std::vector<T>& v) const {
27 return v.capacity() >= minimum_capacity_;
28 }
29
30 private:
31 size_t minimum_capacity_;
32};
33
34} // namespace webrtc
35
36#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_RENDER_QUEUE_ITEM_VERIFIER_H__
